description: This is a language translation tool, it can help you to quickly translate text, document, web page, etc. from English to French and vice versa. It can also help you to detect the language of the text, identify the language of the web page and translate the content of the web page. it can translate text in real-time, you can also save the translation as a file. it can translate any type of text, including legal documents, medical texts, technical texts, news articles, social media posts, etc.

full_summary:
# Electronic Supplier Bidding Orientation
A step in enhancing our procurement workflow, Farm Credit Canada has partnered with the Canadian leader in providing secure electronic access to tenders and RFPs, MERX.

On **Monday, June 26th**, at **1pm CST (English)** and **2pm CST (French)**, we are hosting an orientation webinar for vendors and potential suppliers. This session will support registration and understanding of the MERX platform, which will enable suppliers to compete in electronic bidding.

The webinar can be joined via this link: [https://us06web.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_u4O9CHjqRsC7vuKPjavb9w#/registration](https://us06web.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_u4O9CHjqRsC7vuKPjavb9w#/registration)

For further details on supplying to Farm Credit Canada, kindly contact Procurement@fcc-fac.ca.

**Important Tender Details**

* Solicitation Number: FCC-FAC-GENERAL-002
* Tender Reference Number: CB-6463-42089398
* Tender Status: Expired
* Tender Closing Date: June 27th, 2023, 01:59 AM (UTC)
* Expected Contract Start Date: June 26th, 2023
* Expected Contract End Date: June 26th, 2023

Our procurement process seeks to follow fairness, transparency, and due process guidelines. We encourage all potential suppliers to participate in this orientation as we strive to streamline our workflow and invitewell-established suppliers like you to offer your services.


**Procurement Category**: Services
**Procurement Method**: Competitive Open Bidding
**Trade Agreements**: Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA), Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
**Regions of Opportunity**: Canada
**Regions of Delivery**: Canada
**Tender Description**: This tender involves an orientation and information session regarding the MERX platform, to enable suppliers to compete in electronic bidding.

Note that this revamped text is a concise representation of the original text. I did not include all the information as it was redundant, but not crucial to the context. I also restructured some sentences to improve the readability and give the entry a more professional tone.
